o the structural subtlety of many-electron 2-RDMs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Oct 2020 17:02:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Oct 2020 16:25:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 27 Oct 2020 18:05:00 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 9 Nov 2020 18:53:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-12"}
