 times and decreases monotonically with time. Inhomogeneous\nsupernova explosions are the cause of an asymmetric shape of the gas cloud,\nfacilitating the development of instabilities and the decrease of the cold gas\nfraction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Oct 2020 18:02:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-18"}
