\ncharacteristics is also examined. Transition to local transport at high N$_2$\nadmixture concentrations and long spatial domains is observed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Oct 2020 18:45:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-21"}
