core-less, quite unlike the core-halo structure observed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Oct 2020 15:00:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Oct 2020 18:29:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 19 Jan 2021 09:16:08 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 17 Dec 2021 08:39:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-20"}
