f the results is provided based on a\nhierarchy between orbitals, with $d_{xy}$ driving the spin order, while\nelectronic repulsion and the effective one dimensionality of the movement\nwithin the $d_{xz}$ and $d_{yz}$ orbitals driving the orbital order.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Oct 2020 15:06:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-20"}
